Name: Finger Jets
About the game: Finger Jets: Phase Challenge is a 2D Arcade physics game where you control the Jets of your Spaceship with your Finger tips as you Challenge 3 phases with 6 levels each. Play the levels casually, or in a challenge mode Time Attack where you can rank yourself on the all-time leaderboards. Dodge and burn your way past various obstacles as you collect coins and land on the landing pads. Little bit of a throw back to lunar lander, but mostly a unique concept. Game supports controller input, keyboard, mouse or touch. There are only 2 inputs so use what you like.
